 Daugava|Daugava Daugavpils]]\n|align=\"center\"|21\n|-\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\"  |3\n| {{flagicon|Latvia}} Jur\u0123is Kalns\n| [[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]]\n|align=\"center\"|16\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Latvia}} [[Vladislavs Kozlovs]]\n| [[FK Jelgava|Jelgava]]\n|align=\"center\"|16\n|-\n|align=\"center\" |4\n| {{flagicon|Russia}} [[Vadim Yanchuk]]\n| [[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]]\n|align=\"center\"|12\n|-\n|align=\"center\" |5\n| {{flagicon|Latvia}} [[Vladimirs Kame\u0161s]]\n| [[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]]\n|align=\"center\"|11\n|-\n|}\n\n==Awards==\n\n===Team of the Tournament===\n\n''sportacentrs.com'' version:''<ref name=\"sportacentrs.com\">http://sportacentrs.com/futbols/lmt_virsliga/17112011-sportacentrs_com_virsligas_simboliska_izl{{dead link|date=June 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n\n{| cellpadding=0 cellspacing=1 border=0 \n|- align=center bgcolor=#f2f2f2\n| width=25% | '''Goalkeepers'''\n| width=25% | '''Defenders'''\n| width=25% | '''Midfielders'''\n| width=25% | '''Forwards'''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[P\u0101vels \u0160teinbors]] ([[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]])\n| {{flagicon|GEO}} [[Giorgi Chikradze]] ([[FK Daugava Daugavpils|Daugava Daugavpils]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Val\u0113rijs Afanasjevs]] ([[FK Daugava Daugavpils|Daugava Daugavpils]])\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Nathan J\u00fanior Soares de Carvalho|Nathan J\u00fanior]] ([[Skonto FC|Skonto Riga]])\n|-\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Aleksandrs Vlasovs]] ([[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]])\n| {{flagicon|LTU}} [[Marius \u010cinikas]] ([[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[O\u013cegs Laiz\u0101ns]] ([[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]])\n| {{flagicon|GEO}} Mamuka Ghonghadze ([[FK Daugava Daugavpils|Daugava Daugavpils]])\n|-\n| \n| {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Evgeny Postnikov]] ([[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Aleksandrs Fertovs]] ([[Skonto FC|Skonto Riga]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Vladislavs Kozlovs]] ([[FK Jelgava|Jelgava]])\n\n|'''Coach:''' {{flagicon|GEO}} [[Tamaz Pertia]] ([[FK Daugava Daugavpils|Daugava Daugavpils]]/[[JFK Olimps/RFS|Olimps]])\n|-\n|\n| {{flagicon|NGR}} [[Daniel Ola]] ([[FC J\u016brmala|J\u016brmala]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Gen\u0101dijs Solo\u0146icins]] ([[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} Jur\u0123is Kalns ([[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]])\n|-\n|\n| {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Georgi Ulyanov]] ([[FK Daugava Daugavpils|Daugava Daugavpils]])\n| {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Konstantin Belov]] ([[FC J\u016brmala|J\u016brmala]])\n| \n|-\n|\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Ritvars Rugins]] ([[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Mihails Zizi\u013cevs]] ([[FK Daugava Daugavpils|Daugava Daugavpils]])\n| \n|}\n\n__________________________________________________________________________________________________\n\n''[[Latvian Football Federation]] version:''<ref>http://www.lff.lv/lv/news/2011/nov/23/</ref>\n\n{| cellpadding=0 cellspacing=1 border=0 \n|- align=center bgcolor=#f2f2f2\n| width=25% | '''Goalkeepers'''\n| width=25% | '''Defenders'''\n| width=25% | '''Midfielders'''\n| width=25% | '''Forwards'''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Germans M\u0101li\u0146\u0161]] ([[Skonto FC|Skonto Riga]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[P\u0101vels Sur\u0146ins]] ([[FK Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs|Liep\u0101jas Metalurgs]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Val\u0113rijs Afanasjevs]] ([[FK Daugava Daugavpils|Daugava Daugavpils]])\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Nathan J\u00fanior Soares de Carvalho|Nathan J\u00fanior]] ([[Skonto FC|Skonto Riga]])\n|-\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Aleksandrs Vlasovs]] ([[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Antons Kurakins]] ([[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Ritvars Rugins]] ([[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]])\n| {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Vadim Yanchuk]] ([[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]])\n|-\n| \n| {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Evgeny Postnikov]] ([[FK Ventspils|Ventspils]])\n| {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Aleksandrs Fertovs]]